<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
     <meta charset="UTF-8">
     <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
     <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
     <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/home.css">
     <title>Gainen - where ideas come to life</title>
</head>

<body>
     <header>
          <div class="logo">
               <h2 class="title">Gainen</h2>
               <p class="caption">where ideas come to life</p>
          </div>
          <div class="navbar">
               <ul>
                    <li><a href="/postIdea">Create Idea</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/publicIdea">All Ideas</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/logout">Logout</a></li>
               </ul>
          </div>
     </header>
     <aside class="left">
          <form name="deleteProfile" action="" method="POST">

               Are you sure you want to delete your profile, <%= username %>?<br>

               This is an awesome platform to fund your ideas, but still if you would like to delete your profile
               we assure you that the following details would be deleted from our database:<br>

                    First Name: <%= firstName %><br>
                    Last Name: <%= lastName %><br>
                    Email Id: <%= emailId %><br>
                    Phone Number: <%= phone %><br>
                    Profile Pic:
                    <img src="/profile_pics/<%= profilePicName %>" alt="User Profile Pic" width="100" height="100">
                    <button type="submit">Delete Profile</button>
          </form>
     </aside>
     <main></main>
     <footer>
          <p class="footerText">&copy; 2021 Gainen. All rights reserved.</p>
     </footer>
</body>

</html>